 <br>
Now Lord Rak'Ashiir drops a book that I need to give to the Spirit Sentinel to fix my faction.<br>
<br>
Also if we run into any of the following in the City of Mist, I need for my epic as well. Personal Diary Page, Crier's Scroll, Merchant's Letter, Written Announcement, Priest's Diary Page, Student's Log.<br>
All are found on Skeletons, Golems and Goos at the zone and the Student's log is found on a Spectral Courier.<br>
<br>
